## Arrow Semantics

| Arrow / wrapper | Meaning | Avoid implying |
|---|---|---|
| Block arrow | High-level transformation or separation | Fine-grained causality |
| Iterative wrapper | Panels update together | One-pass pipeline |
| Final readout | Available after convergence | Intermediate posterior is final |

